---
const cols = [
  {
    title: "Hizmetler",
    links: [
      { href: "#yontem", label: "Yöntem" },
      { href: "#paketler", label: "Paketler" },
      { href: "#kimin-icin", label: "Kimler için" },
      { href: "#sss", label: "SSS" }
    ]
  },
  {
    title: "Stack",
    links: [
      { href: "#", label: "n8n" },
      { href: "#", label: "Telegram Bot API" },
      { href: "#", label: "Twenty CRM" },
      { href: "#", label: "Ollama" }
    ]
  },
  {
    title: "Postfabrica",
    links: [
      { href: "/manifesto", label: "Manifesto" },
      { href: "https://github.com/shakg/postfabrica-landing-page", label: "GitHub" },
      { href: "#iletisim", label: "İletişim" },
      { href: "mailto:merhaba@postfabrica.co", label: "merhaba@postfabrica.co" }
    ]
  }
];
---

<footer class="bg-paper border-t border-line">
  <div class="container-wide py-16">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <a href="#top" class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
          <span class="size-7 rounded-full bg-ink grid place-items-center text-paper text-[10px] font-mono tracking-tighter">
            P/
          </span>
          <span class="font-medium tracking-tight">postfabrica</span>
          <span class="text-muted text-xs font-mono ml-1">.co</span>
        </a>

        <p class="mt-5 text-sm text-ink/70 leading-relaxed max-w-sm">
          Türkiye’deki KOBİ’ler için saha odaklı AI otomasyon ortağı. WhatsApp, Excel ve dağınık araçlar arasında kalan işi görünür, ölçülebilir ve sahiplenilebilir akışlara dönüştürür.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-muted font-mono">
          © 2026 Postfabrica · İstanbul
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        {
          cols.map((c) => (
            <div>
              <p class="label mb-3">{c.title}</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-ink/70">
                {c.links.map((l) => (
                  <li>
                    <a href={l.href} class="hover:text-ink transition-colors">
                      {l.label}
                    </a>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-line flex flex-col md:flex-row items-start md:items-center justify-between gap-3 text-xs text-muted font-mono">
      <p>Postfabrica · saha odaklı otomasyon · Türkiye</p>
      <p>Andrea Branzi’nin Post-Fabbrica konseptinden esinlenilmiştir.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
